{"tid":727220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得夏天行山唔係無腦就係自殺","createTime":"2018-07-03T01:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T04:07:52.000Z","uid":123613,"like":10,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba187fa3e0834cae737ba815129633804b6d3fe5","tid":727220,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T01:05:02.000Z","msg":"放假行山已經on9，晨咁早就要起身，大把人一個星期得一日假，係人都想瞓到中午先起身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夏天行山仲on9，唔係熱死就行雷落雨，將心比己，萬一出事又係咪煩到消防員，累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴日咁個天氣行山擺明唔係無腦就係自殺，正常人係唔需要同情一個無腦或者想去自殺既人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f25a89b5b0713b2f8109a3ea3641c51e0dc9c5","tid":727220,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T01:05:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"506c4c5830bb622291f8ed8ec0512d22020a7b20","tid":727220,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99f25a89b5b0713b2f8109a3ea3641c51e0dc9c5","tid":727220,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T01:05:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T01:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b404b9a787ff6ec90a3318267fe5e8ff0fd729a5","tid":727220,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf29cf3f98280e12bdb9c7669bb8eb60f9538e2","tid":727220,"uid":179938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"唔覺<br />\n利申: 40℃照行冇死到"},{"pid":"d9582cabc6649c7185471320644fa203cee323c2","tid":727220,"uid":117896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"覺 ， 仲要被雷劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}